@startuml mebaysan_Modern-Data-Architecture
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "User" as User

rectangle "Local CSV Files" as CSV #aliceblue

rectangle "Airbyte" as Airbyte #lightsteelblue

rectangle "Python Script" as PyScript #palegreen

rectangle "PostgreSQL" as Postgres #mistyrose

rectangle "DBT" as DBT #lightyellow

rectangle "Apache Superset" as Superset #lavender

rectangle "Nginx" as Nginx #peachpuff

' ========== Deployment Flow ==========
User -> CSV : Provides dataset
CSV -> Airbyte : Ingests data via\nAirbyte connector
CSV -> PyScript : Alternative data loading\n(if Airbyte not used)
PyScript -> Postgres : Loads data directly
Airbyte -> Postgres : Loads transformed data
Postgres -> DBT : Performs data modeling\nand transformations
DBT -> Postgres : Stores transformed data
Postgres -> Superset : Connects for visualization
Superset <-> Nginx : Optional reverse proxy\nfor pgAdmin access
@enduml